snippet.textDisplay: This season was truly a journey of Pakistan. We started from the southern most area of Sindh, went to Peshawar, explored the streets of Gharviwalla mohalla, rode on trains, went back to the 60s, took a short trip to Norway and ended at the extreme North of Pakistan in Swat. If only we could have such people with great hearts and sincerity running the country. Beyond words!
